{"tid":1382319,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"一切還原基本步","createTime":"2019-07-29T12:34:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-29T12:41:39.000Z","uid":159651,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"4b4d04e2d2eb9a832125d76d0994572e14919d33","tid":1382319,"uid":159651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T12:34:59.000Z","msg":"講得難聽叫和理非，講得好聽叫拖延時間比前線。<br />\n<br />\n經過一個幾月，相信大家唔多唔少心又累身都好累。經過尋日一戰，更多前線手足比人拉咗，前線拉一個少一個，心痛得黎仲令人懷疑無咗班前線依場抗爭仲可唔可以持續落去。<br />\n<br />\n大家記唔記得依場夢嘅起初我地嘅戰術係乜？&mdash;&mdash;<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">游擊戰</span></strong></span><br />\n當時以消耗狗隻體力為重點，有人提出每次等到狗上晒裝就散。而我認為，我地要還原基本步，打返游擊戰，<strong><span style=\"color: green;\">每次引到啲狗仔上晒裝就返屋企食飯</span></strong><br />\n你可能會話：「兄弟爬山」我會話：「前線仲可以爬多幾多次，前線同和理非嘅人數比例懸殊，每次都係勇武保護和理非，點解依家唔可以調返轉」<br />\n你可能會話：「每次都一上裝就散無人衝，仲點會繼續落去」我會話：「我地比少少時間打輿論戰，可以繼續做到維持民憤同社會國際關注嘅效果」<br />\n你可能會話：「等到幾時，每一次都係最後一次」我會話：「唔係想減弱士氣，但我相信有唔少人同我一樣都覺得<span style=\"color: red;\">十月一係終極一戰</span>，而係十一之前，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">我地一個都不能再少</span></span></span>」<br />\n<br />\n請前線善用和理非嘅力量，爭取一個星期嘅時間又好，一日嘅時間都好，好好休息，好好裝備自己，好好傾戰略。希望前線知道，一班和理非永遠都係到，你地衝，我地尊重亦心痛。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">「光復香港，時代革命」</span></strong></span><br />\n唔可以再只係口號，我地一定要成功<br />\n<br />\n只係表達自己意見，歡迎戰略討論"},{"pid":"99f168e305a10acbabf1bf746b05bfbe8aed5da6","tid":1382319,"uid":159651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T12:35:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d852f62b9ad4f5de347eb0ce6ef212788ad7d0f6","tid":1382319,"uid":159651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T12:35:27.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1a978d6b8bd2ecef07b2a7ac91670ac02df73688","tid":1382319,"uid":159651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T12:35:38.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"323d6cbe8c21f93802bf47bc3ca2f336c7ec4866","tid":1382319,"uid":159651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T12:36:05.000Z","msg":"推比勇武手足睇下可行性"},{"pid":"62e591b8b7f1af48f858966d9f06a126231ac1e6","tid":1382319,"uid":159651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T12:36:36.000Z","msg":"光復香港，時代革命"},{"pid":"b17cc8b4528b3b640725bc5848235205ea84ca57","tid":1382319,"uid":159651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T12:36:54.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"025827c5a6e569eef2859f4dbb3ea4da5a5d4965","tid":1382319,"uid":159651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T12:37:05.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"8d58d0b0770092308f8b4245024ee1e9063b96ff","tid":1382319,"uid":159651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T12:38:40.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"42de4c6dc0fd80e68120e052a0c6a6560dda095b","tid":1382319,"uid":159651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T12:38:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2f6ca827bb8c5ef01cca86256ba508bc2d06ef8","tid":1382319,"uid":159651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T12:41:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}